The paper focuses on the analysis of transmit beamforming schemes with a low-rate feedback link in wireless sensor/relay networks, which involves information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
